document.title: Pinkhof Medisch Woordenboek (Online)
document.intro: The printed version of the Pinkhof Geneeskundig Woordenboek (Pinkhof Medical Dictionary) was first published in 1923. This famous resource was originally compiled by the Herman Pinkhof, GP in Amsterdam and has seen many updates and reprints since then. This online version contains more ...
